DATA.virtual_field_sql_1:
SELECT 
	CASE
		WHEN cp.cdb_object_id IS NULL THEN 0
		WHEN p.name_de!=cp.name_de THEN 0
		WHEN p.name_en!=cp.name_en THEN 0
		WHEN p.erp_code!=cp.sap_property THEN 0
		WHEN p.data_type!=cp.data_type THEN 0
		WHEN (
			SELECT MIN(se.sync_status)
			FROM (
		SELECT
			CASE
				WHEN ce.catalogue_property_object_id IS NULL THEN 0
				WHEN e.value_txt_de != ce.value_txt_de THEN 0
				WHEN e.value_txt_en != ce.value_txt_en THEN 0
				WHEN e.name != ce.name THEN 0
				ELSE 1
			END sync_status,
			e.product_object_id, e.id
		FROM cdbvp_enum_def e
		LEFT JOIN cdbvp_catalogue_enum_def ce
		ON e.catalogue_property_object_id = ce.catalogue_property_object_id
		AND e.catalog_enum_value=ce.value
			) se
			WHERE (p.product_object_id=se.product_object_id AND p.id=se.id)
		)=0 THEN 0
		ELSE 1
	END sync_status
FROM cdbvp_property p
LEFT JOIN cdbvp_catalogue_property cp
ON p.catalogue_property_object_id = cp.cdb_object_id
WHERE p.product_object_id=cdbvp_property.product_object_id AND p.id=cdbvp_property.id
